Usage: selectPtnPinGuide [-help] <{llx lly urx ury}> <pinGuideName>
                         <metalLayer> <minSpace> [<pinGroupCell>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<{llx lly urx ury}>     # Specifies the lower left x and y , upper right x and
                        # y coordinates of the pin guide. (box, required)
<pinGuideName>          # Specifies name of the pin, wildcard can be specified
                        # (string, required)
<metalLayer>            # Specifies the layer on which the pin guide resides.
                        # (string, required)
<minSpace>              # Specifies the minimum pin spacing for the pin guide.
                        # (int, required)
<pinGroupCell>          # Specifies the cell name if the pin guide is
                        # associated with a cell pin group. (string, optional)